public class GoldCardFront extends PlayerAreaCard
ingsw.codex_naturalis.model.cards.initialResourceGold.front.Front side of the GoldCard Each card could contain Resources or Objects in the Corners There isn't any central resource Each GoldCard has a list of Symbols that the Player has to have into his PlayerArea in order to be able to place the card
